	<name>Dynamic Wallpaper Creator</name>
	  <summary>Simple dynamic wallpaper creator</summary>
	  <description>
	    <p>A program for creating dynamic wallpapers from a sequence of individual static images.  As a result of the program, a file in XML format is obtained, which can be specified as wallpaper in the additional settings of the GNOME environment.</p>
	  </description>
